As of July 2014, SAIU was structured into four colleges:<ref>{{cite web| url=http://gs.saiu.ac.ug/index.php/colleges |title=Saint Augustine Internationaal University: College|accessdate=6 July 2017|date=6 July 2017 | location=Kampala |author=SAIU |publisher=St. Augustine International University (SAIU)}}</ref> # College of Law and Business # College of Agriculture and Veterinary Medicine # College of Engineering and Information Sciences # College of Health, Medicine and Life Sciences
